        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " by: Primo Levi. It's a haunting and remarkably well-written autobiographical account of Levi surviving Auschwitz in his mid-twenties. It’s (obviously) a pretty dark, and extremely moving book; one that I can't recommend enough.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.amazon.com/This-Man-Truce-Primo-Levi/dp/0349100136"
        }
